entType().getRawClass()).isSameAs(Integer.class);\n        assertThat(((ArrayType) integerArrayType).getEmptyArray()).isEmpty();\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1142, "output": 581, "cacheRead": 19456, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 21179, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780700265401, "responseId": "resp_0dbfa1d2b7716c48016a235469d6ac8194b2146373fbc8dbfc"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_Rot8XKCeoS0im4ihAJLZIVlz|fc_0dbfa1d2b7716c48016a23546dbdb881948b5cfe185df8b4b3", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1663 bytes to tests/src/com.fasterxml.jackson.core/jackson-databind/2.22.0/src/test/java/com_fasterxml_jackson_core/jackson_databind/ArrayTypeTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780700274232}]}
